data.Name: Abhisri.M
data.Description:
"Passion is full of energy and enthusiasm
that takes you to the next beautiful venture of life."
Passion brought me to Astro Club, where I can drift my thoughts into the enigma of space with my club members.

data.Name: Syed Junaid Ali B
data.Description: I am pursuing my Computer science degree and always interested to learn new and innovative stuff. One is from the filed of computer science, another is space.

data.Name: Sarvesh
data.Description: I am an ardent astrophile who is obsessed with space.  I like to learn about various astronomical objects, particularly bizarre ones.  I feel that it is the conjunction of various domains which makes astronomy beautiful.

data.Name: Narendran G
data.Description: Astrophile! If you think your life is meaningless, then know that we are living in a universe where we are of plank length significance. Enjoy it while you can!

data.Name: Nisha Pa
data.Description: I'm just a person standing in front of a donut, asking it to be a salad.

data.Name: Puvis K
data.Description: A sophomore majoring in Computer Science and Engineering. Enchanted by the vastness of space and the stars in it , I got curious to delve into  galactic and extragalactic astronomy. Daydreaming and stargazing from then till now C:

data.Name: Shiny R V
data.Description: I love space; Not just because of it's infinite beauty, or the way it works with such well defined laws. I love space because it's the only thing that holds as many secrets as I do

data.Name: Jayesh S
data.Description: I am pursuing my undergraduate in biotechnology. I love to work as a team and solve problems. I find myself interested in astronomical observation.

data.Name: Aishwarya G
data.Description: I am an astrophile and star gazing makes me feel so relaxed. I was always interested in space and I do believe that solving the mysteries of space is important as it might be of some use to solve the problems we have on Earth as well. As a student pursuing Biotechnology and my passion for space exploration makes me curious and want to learn more about the space biology and the space biotechnology which is a budding field.

data.Name: Vishal R
data.Description: Self-motivated individual with immense love for sciences. Space enthusiast with eyes fixed on stars. Loves stargazing whenever I feel low. Always been interested in the mysteries of the universe.

data.Name: Mohana Priya M K
data.Description: Exploring deepest curating concepts of space and different mediums of art to find my own. There is only one rule about brushes: more. Pursuing biotech...

data.Name: Rishi S
data.Description: Extremely enthusiastic enigma with the eagerness and ease to embrace the experience even its chaos on the extraterrestrial or the interstellar. A person with immense Love for Galaxies, because the universe is my crush.

data.Name: Shershon A J
data.Description: Two things always capture my attention. The way the universe unravels itself in front of our naked eyes and the way we have been unravelling its mysteries and communicating it through the generations, since time immemorial. Exhilarated that I could get the taste of both and contribute my part to the ever-growing astrophile community.

data.Name: Ananya K
data.Description: A highly motivated bibliophile who strongly believes that the real world exists where aliens are! Trust me, all that you need is a little space :)
